  <preparation>Mix together flour, baking powder and salt.  Sift over combined fruit and nuts and toss..  Cream butter then cream in sugar, and eggs one at a time.  Add lemon extract, stir in floured fruit, lastly add fruit juice.  

Line pan with wax paper.  Prepare oven with steam pan.  Bake 1 1/2 hrs at 300F before reducing heat to 250F for another half hour.</preparation>
